critical stiffness.\nDifferences appear for large faults where rupture propagation is important,\nthough differences might still be negligible for many applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 22:45:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-24"}
